querylist.query: select code,name,descript,parentcode,compcode from codemst where code like 'dv%' and compcode=@comp

if exists (select * from codemst where code=@code) 
begin	 
update codemst set code=@code,name=@name,descript=@desc,parentcode=@pcode,compcode=@comp	  where code=@code
end    
else begin	  
insert codemst (code,name,descript,parentcode,compcode) values (@code,@name,@desc,@pcode,@comp)   
 end
